80.7008, 79.6323, 79.7397, 77.7467, 77.1211, 75.9619, 74.5401, 76.5165, 76.5291, 77.7941, 76.632, 75.5518, 75.7491, 76.8565, 76.5173, 77.2397, 77.3316, 77.2171, 76.4863, 75.9551, 76.6483, 79.5171, 79.8656, 80.2751, 81.2287, 81.8601, 81.9017, 82.1191, 80.7652, 79.2148, 78.4007, 76.6395, 75.6597, 75.5374, 76.5204, 77.5608, 79.1503, 81.4708, 80.832, 81.4802, 82.9957, 84.1616, 82.9461, 85.7283, 90.0746, 90.3602, 90.6867, 92.0868, 95.4131, 103.2361, 96.0181, 100.2232, 104.2221, 102.9141, 104.4599, 105.1828, 107.0018, 107.0888, 108.1975, 107.3108, 105.9237, 103.4274, 105.3442, 103.4187, 101.3896, 100.7528, 98.2189, 101.6385, 101.1063, 101.3486, 100.0489, 102.6104, 103.2527, 103.2891, 102.3045, 101.3108, 101.2995, 101.3781, 101.04, 100.633, 100.3539, 100.7698, 101.8928, 101.7869, 102.5675, 103.1713, 102.6416, 102.7674, 102.2678, 102.2325, 102.4485, 101.9967, 101.5352, 101.2277, 101.1777, 100.3913, 101.3874], "summary_html": "<h1>持续异常交易量因子 PATV</h1>\n<p><strong>Sharpe 0.87 | 通过 0.8 阈值（R6 deep-iterate）</strong></p>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>PATV（Persistent Abnormal Trading Volume）因子衡量交易量异常的<strong>持续性</strong>。传统异常交易量因子 ATV 仅捕捉短期成交量与长期中枢的偏离，但零星的异常交易量无法形成确定性的反转趋势。PATV 的核心逻辑是：异常交易的持续性越强，非理性情绪主导的时间越长，累积的价格偏差越大，未来反转修正幅度也越大。因此 PATV 值越高的品种未来表现越差（负向因子）。</p>\n<p>在商品期货上，该因子利用日频成交量数据构建。高 PATV 品种做空、低 PATV 品种做多，通过截面多空获取收益。</p>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>Step 1 — 异常交易量 ATV:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ATV}_t = \\frac{\\text{MA}_{20}(\\text{Volume}_t)}{\\text{MA}_{240}(\\text{Volume}_t)}</div>\n<p><strong>Step 2 — 截面排名:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank\\_ATV}_t = \\text{CrossSectionalRank}(\\text{ATV}_t) \\in [0, 1]</div>\n<p><strong>Step 3 — 持续异常交易量 PATV_d:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{PATV}_d = \\frac{\\mu_{pw}(\\text{rank\\_ATV})}{\\sigma_{pw}(\\text{rank\\_ATV})} + \\text{Kurt}_{pw}(\\text{rank\\_ATV})</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\mu_{pw}</span>、<span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{pw}</span> 和 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{Kurt}_{pw}</span> 分别为滚动 <span class=\"math-tex\">pw</span> 日的均值、标准差和超额峰度。</p>\n<p><strong>Step 4 — EMA 平滑:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{PATV} = \\text{EMA}_{20}(\\text{PATV}_d)</div>\n<p><strong>仓位:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position} = -\\text{rank\\_to\\_ls}(\\text{PATV}) \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{target}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{realized}}</div>\n<h2>参数列表</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认值</th><th>范围</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>atv_short_window</code></td><td>20</td><td>[5, 60]</td><td>ATV 短期均线窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>atv_long_window</code></td><td>240</td><td>[60, 480]</td><td>ATV 长期均线窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>persist_window</code></td><td>60</td><td>[20, 120]</td><td>持续性统计滚动窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>ema_span</code></td><td>20</td><td>[5, 60]</td><td>EMA 平滑参数</td></tr><tr><td><code>rebal_days</code></td><td>20</td><td>[5, 60]</td><td>再平衡周期（交易日）</td></tr><tr><td><code>vol_target</code></td><td>0.15</td><td>[0.05, 0.30]</td><td>年化波动率目标</td></tr><tr><td><code>max_leverage</code></td><td>2.0</td><td>[0.5, 5.0]</td><td>最大杠杆</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe（扣费后）</td><td><strong>0.8684</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>52.7%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-34.1%</td></tr><tr><td>Max Corr（因子库）</td><td>0.136（新信号）</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>Top 5 变体（R6）</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>变体</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>年化收益</th><th>最大回撤</th></tr><tr><td>r6_excl_b5_win_h15_raw</td><td>0.8684</td><td>52.7%</td><td>-34.1%</td></tr><tr><td>r6_excl_b5_raw</td><td>0.8293</td><td>49.2%</td><td>-40.6%</td></tr><tr><td>r6_excl_b5_win_q25_raw</td><td>0.7845</td><td>51.7%</td><td>-55.5%</td></tr><tr><td>r6_excl_b5_win_ema15_raw</td><td>0.7784</td><td>46.9%</td><td>-52.1%</td></tr><tr><td>r6_excl_b5_win_h30_raw</td><td>0.7682</td><td>47.0%</td><td>-30.6%</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>基础实现，pw=20/40/60 + EMA(10/20/40) 网格</td><td>实现ATV和PATV全部因子，6个变体</td><td>patv_60_raw=0.6921，pw=60最优</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>R1用了vol_ma20/vol_ma240做ATV，R2误改为volume/vol_ma240</td><td>扩展pw到80/120 + EMA改为半窗口 + 更长hold</td><td>下降到0.5717（公式变更导致退步）</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>恢复正确ATV公式 + 展开更多EMA和hold组合</td><td>10个变体网格搜索</td><td>0.6381，仍低于R1</td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td>Pipeline自动回退到R1 spec_best</td><td>无操作</td><td>恢复到0.6921</td></tr><tr><td>R5</td><td>在R1基础上增加离散L/S信号 + hold网格 + IC gate</td><td>rank_to_ls替代rank_to_continuous</td><td>0.7079（新高）</td></tr><tr><td>R6</td><td>R5 亏损品种集中（YY/SF/B/L/RU） + 截面尾部噪声放大</td><td>bottom-5 exclude + CS winsorize(MAD=5) + fine grid (pw/ema/hold/long_q)</td><td><strong>0.8684</strong>（通过 0.8 阈值）</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>R5 引入离散化L/S信号（只做top/bottom 20%）替代连续信号，Sharpe 从 0.6921 提升到 0.7079。</li>\n<li>R6 做了三件事：(a) 直接剔除持续亏损的 5 个品种（YY/SF/B/L/RU），消除结构性负贡献；(b) MAD=5 截面 winsorize 压缩峰度尾部（PATV 公式含 kurtosis，极端值会污染 rank）；(c) 精细 hold 网格发现 hold=15 优于 hold=20。最大回撤同时从 -63.6% 降到 -34.1%（近乎减半），说明不仅 Sharpe 提升，风险特征也显著改善。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全部商品期货（约59个活跃品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 20个交易日（月度换仓）</li>\n<li><strong>信号方向</strong>: 负向（高PATV做空，低PATV做多）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 原报告使用5分钟高频数据计算日内持续性，此处用日频数据近似，信号粒度有损失\n<p>- 截面IC较低（~0.004），信号主要通过截面分散化 + 极值剔除获取收益 - R6 硬编码剔除了 5 个亏损品种（YY/SF/B/L/RU），有一定样本内过拟合风险，需OOS 验证其稳定性</p>"}